{"tid":1149604,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)天龍特攻隊 直航殺機 高凶三萬尺 邊個殺我隻狗1-2","createTime":"2019-05-11T09:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T16:56:30.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f3602db5ac30f3ecaf481f96cd7df6e108ac4b","tid":1149604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=16bf55d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=8080184d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=edbb03d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bc/The_A-Team.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbc%2FThe_A-Team.jpg&h=4aadffa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/2d/Flightplan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F2d%2FFlightplan.jpg&h=a7a54bda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/Non-Stop2014Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2FNon-Stop2014Poster.jpg&h=54f12a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.同樣身為美國陸軍遊騎兵，約翰&middot;&quot;漢尼拔&quot;&middot;史密斯、派克&middot;斐斯、拜庫斯&middot;博斯克和默多克四人曾經在墨西哥和黑暗勢力鬥爭時結成好友，組成了「天龍特攻隊」。一日，美國將軍莫里森找到他們，請他們幫助美國軍方找回丟失在伊拉克戰爭中的美元鈔票模板，四人在伊拉克巴格達找到了假冒的美元鈔票模板，卻被幕後人物布拉德&middot;帕克奪走，而天龍特攻隊也因被誣陷而關進了監獄..<br />\n<br />\n2.女主角凱莉‧普雷是一位在柏林工作的航空工程師，不久前丈夫離奇的跌落窗外過世，留下她與六歲的女兒茱莉亞。為了將丈夫的靈柩運回美國。不過，在旅程的E-474客機上，起飛後，睡了一覺醒來凱莉卻發現女兒不見了，不但機上也沒人記得她帶了女兒上飛機，艙單裡也沒有茱莉亞的登機的紀錄。就在凱莉找回女兒的過程中，她也逐漸發現了一個巨大的陰謀&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n3.美國聯邦航空局空中乘警比爾&middot;馬克斯，與同事傑克&middot;哈蒙在一架紐約飛往倫敦的波音767飛機上執行秘密反恐維安任務，一位風情萬種的美麗熟女珍&middot;薩默斯調換靠窗座位至比爾身邊。飛行期間有佳人相伴，原本比爾相當開心，但隨即狀況改變。比爾收到一系列神秘劫匪發送的威脅簡訊，對方不僅洞悉他的身份與嗜好，甚至威脅他如不要求美國政府以網路銀行向一個神秘帳戶轉入1.5億美元，就會每二十分鐘殺死一個乘客。比爾剛開始誤以為這是一向行事骯髒的哈蒙所搞的陰謀，但通過會面他而檢查他的手機後發現不是他..<br />\n<br />\n4.約翰&middot;維克是一位退隱江湖的殺手，不久前失去了因病而逝的妻子海倫，這令他哀傷不已，舉辦完葬禮後連過去同為殺手的馬克斯也前來關心他。不久後，約翰收到了一隻海倫生前為他訂的小狗黛西，海倫希望黛西能陪伴約翰，而他也將黛西視為朋友。一早，約翰開著他69年的福特野馬愛車和黛西出門，當到一間加油站加油時，塔拉索夫家族的領頭維果的兒子約謝夫想要和約翰買下他的車，但被約翰拒絕，約謝夫便此心生不滿。當晚，約謝夫和另外兩位朋友格雷戈里、維克多蒙面闖入約翰家中，不但襲擊了他還殺死了黛西..<br />\n<br />\n5.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面..<br />\n<br />\n5 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=f36e18d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=45576265\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af37782f67d0ef29a1fb6ce507796331383600de","tid":1149604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7205f3677da0ba9f9feb647b63fe35259ec51703","tid":1149604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784d57c33ddfe4187acd1e6a30d252bb965d1d88","tid":1149604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be79626ab21758019768560d8aa5f43522c8738","tid":1149604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcee9c252ce720bba271d62cbd4417c31a75fc1","tid":1149604,"uid":29160